_sText:
Updated, fixed & a longer map! Tested it with a few friends of mine and now it works 100%! Some parts are detailed and some aren't, my future maps will be fully detailed and theme based. Credits go to 'Massive' for the prefab barn!

In this version I added trig_push so that when you get out of the teleporter, players don't get stuck. (hopefully)

* File Size: 9mb *


P.S.
     
     Some hints are identified by orange half-life logos...
